    ICO Refund Portal

    EVM refunds will take longer than expected. Instant refunds in SOL/USDC are available now. Connect your wallet, verify ownership, and claim your refund.

    1. Your contributing EVM wallet

    Connect the EVM wallet you used to participate in the ICO.

    2. Prove wallet ownership

    Sign a message to verify you own this wallet address.

    3. Your SOL wallet (to receive refund)

    Enter the Solana wallet address where you want to receive your refund.

    Refunds are instant in SOL/USDC after verification.
